# Prolance

- **Auth**: Supabase Auth + JWT; use [`AuthService`](lib/core/services/auth_service.dart). Do not reintroduce password-in-SharedPreferences auth.
- **Routing**: [`GoRouter`](lib/core/navigation/app_router.dart) + `context.go` / `context.push`. Public routes: `/`, `/onboarding`, `/login`, `/register`, `/forgot-password`.
- **Data**: Prefer Supabase tables in [`supabase/migrations/`](supabase/migrations/) with RLS. Job reads go through [`SupabaseJobRepository`](lib/core/repositories/supabase_job_repository.dart).
- **Escrow**: Business logic in [`PaymentService`](lib/core/services/payment_service.dart); optional Edge Function [`supabase/functions/escrow`](supabase/functions/escrow).
- **Tests**: `flutter test`; widget tests must call [`bootstrap()`](lib/main.dart) via `setUpAll` and use `SharedPreferences.setMockInitialValues({})`. Skip `Supabase.initialize` when `WidgetsBinding` is `AutomatedTestWidgetsFlutterBinding` (handled in [`bootstrap`](lib/main.dart)).
- **Web / monorepo**: Next.js apps live under [`packages/landing`](packages/landing) and [`packages/admin`](packages/admin) (npm, not Dart).
